nked to the series page'=>'与 %series_icon% 相同，除了系列图标将链接到系列页面','This token is for use with the orgSeries widget only - it references where you want the list of series titles to be inserted and requires that the template for each series title be also set.'=>'此令牌仅用于 orgSeries widget - 它引用您希望插入系列标题列表的位置，并要求为每个系列标题设置模板。','This will be replaced with the title of a series'=>'这将被替换为系列的标题','Same as %series_title% except that it will also be linked to the series page'=>'同 %series_title%，但它也将链接到系列页面','Is the location token for where the contents of the post list post templates will appear.'=>'是帖子列表帖子模板内容出现的位置令牌。','Is the location token for where the contents of the post list post templates will appear and use provided widget post short title.'=>'是帖子列表帖子模板内容出现的位置令牌，并使用提供的 widget 帖子短标题。','Will be replaced with the post title of a post in the series'=>'将被替换为系列中某个帖子的标题','Will be replaced with the post title of a post in the series linked to the page view of that post.'=>'将被替换为与该帖子的页面视图链接的系列中帖子的标题。','Will be replaced with the post title short of a post in the series'=>'将被替换为系列中某个帖子的短标题','Will be replaced with the post title short of a post in the series linked to the page view of that post.'=>'将被替换为与该帖子的页面视图链接的系列中帖子的短标题。','Will be replaced by the navigation link for the previous post in a series. The text will be whatever is included in the \'Custom Previous Post Navigation Text\' field. If that field is empty then the text will be the title of the post'=>'将被替换为系列中前一个帖子的导航链接。文本将是“自定义前一个帖子导航文本”字段中包含的内容。如果该字段为空，则文本将是帖子的标题。','Will be replaced by the navigation link for the next post in a series. The text will be whatever is included in the \'Custom Next Post Navigation Text\' field. If that field is empty then the text will be the title of the post'=>'将被替换为系列中下一个帖子的导航链接。文本将是“自定义下一个帖子导航文本”字段中包含的内容。如果该字段为空，则文本将是帖子的标题。','Will be replaced by the navigation link for the first post in a series. The text will be whatever is included in the \'Custom First Post Navigation Text\' field. If that field is empty then the text will be the title of the post'=>'将被替换为系列中第一个帖子的导航链接。文本将是“自定义第一个帖子导航文本”字段中包含的内容。如果该字段为空，则文本将是帖子的标题。','Use this tag either before or after the rest of the template code.  It will indicate where you want the content of a post to display.'=>'在模板代码的其余部分之前或之后使用此标签。它将指示您希望帖子内容显示的位置。','Will display what part of a series the post is'=>'将显示该文章在系列中的部分','Will display the total number of posts in a series'=>'将显示系列中的帖子总数','Will display the description for the series'=>'将显示系列的描述','Will output the slug of the series'=>'将输出该系列的别名','Will output the ID of the series'=>'将输出该系列的ID','Will output the author of the post'=>'将输出文章的作者','If the post has a feature-image then that image will be displayed'=>'如果文章有特色图片，则会显示该图片','The date that a post was published'=>'文章发布的日期','Will be replaced with the unpublished post title of a post in the series'=>'将被替换为系列中未发布文章的标题','Will display the total number of published and unpublished posts in a series'=>'将显示系列中已发布和未发布文章的总数','Update Options'=>'更新选项','Clicking Yes will reset the options to the defaults and you will lose all customizations. Or you can click cancel and return.'=>'点击“是”将重置选项为默认值，您将失去所有自定义设置。或者您可以点击取消并返回。','No'=>'否','Yes'=>'是','Please update your PublishPress Series data'=>'请更新您的 PublishPress 系列数据','We have made changes to how series are stored and this requires a small update. This improves support for the Multiple Series feature, and resolves some issues with the order of posts. Please click this button to upgrade.'=>'我们对系列的存储方式进行了更改，这需要进行小幅更新。这改善了对多个系列功能的支持，并解决了一些与帖子顺序相关的问题。请点击此按钮进行升级。','Update Series data'=>'更新系列数据','Series upgrade completed.'=>'系列升级完成。','Series order sync completed. %d posts updated.'=>'系列顺序同步完成。%d 个帖子已更新。','Search Series'=>'搜索系列','Popular Series'=>'热门系列','All Series'=>'所有系列','Edit Series'=>'编辑系列','Update Series'=>'更新系列','Add New Series'=>'添加新系列','New Series Name'=>'新系列名称','No series found'=>'未找到系列','%1$s series migrated from "%2$s" to "%3$s" taxonomy. Settings updated.'=>'%1$s 系列已从 "%2$s" 迁移到 "%3$s" taxonomy。设置已更新。','PublishPress Series Plugin Options have been updated'=>'PublishPress 系列插件选项已更新','Permission denied'=>'权限被拒绝','PublishPress Series Plugin Options have been RESET'=>'PublishPress 系列插件选项已被重置','Please change these settings carefully as they make significant changes to PublishPress Series.'=>'请小心更改这些设置，因为它们会对 PublishPress Series 进行重大更改。','Series Settings'=>'系列设置','Delete all PublishPress Series data from the database when deleting this plugin.'=>'在删除此插件时，从数据库中删除所有 PublishPress Series 数据。','Series Upgrade'=>'系列升级','Run Upgrade Task'=>'运行升级任务','In version 2.11.4, PublishPress Series made changes to how series are stored. You can run the upgrade task here if you\'re having issues with series parts.'=>'在版本 2.11.4 中，PublishPress Series 对系列的存储方式进行了更改。如果您在使用系列部分时遇到问题，可以在这里运行升级任务。','Sync Series Order to Menu Order'=>'同步系列顺序到菜单顺序','Sync to Menu Order'=>'同步到菜单顺序','This will sync all series part numbers to WordPress menu_order field. Useful for themes/page builders that can only sort by menu order (Page Attributes: Order). This allows you to use native WordPress ordering instead of custom fields.'=>'这将同步所有系列部分编号到 WordPress 的 menu_order 字段。对只能按菜单顺序排序的主题/页面构建器非常有用（页面属性：顺序）。这允许您使用原生 WordPress 排序而不是自定义字段。','Reset settings'=>'重置设置','Reset options to default'=>'将选项重置为默认','Legacy'=>'遗留','Legacy Settings'=>'遗留设置','Default'=>'默认','CSS Styles'=>'CSS 样式','Use PublishPress Series CSS styles?'=>'使用 PublishPress 样式吗？','Style options'=>'样式选项','Use default style'=>'使用默认样式','Use box style'=>'使用盒子样式','Use dark style'=>'使用深色样式','Use light style'=>'使用浅色样式','Series Overview'=>'系列概览','Choose the design for the taxonomy page where a single Series is displayed.'=>'选择单个系列显示的分类页面的设计。','Layout:'=>'布局：','Choosing a layout different to "Default" will override the taxonomy template from your theme. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Click here for details on how to customize these designs</a>.'=>'选择不同于“默认”的布局将覆盖您主题中的分类模板。<a href="%s" target="_blank">点击这里查看如何自定义这些设计的详细信息</a>。','Columns:'=>'列：','Order series by:'=>'按以下方式排序系列：','Series part'=>'系列部分','Order by date'=>'按日期排序','Series order method'=>'系列排序方式','Series Table of Contents'=>'系列目录','Series Table of Contents URL:'=>'系列目录 URL：','view page'=>'查看页面','You must %1s update your permalink structure %2s to something other than "Plain" for the Series Table of Contents URL to work.'=>'您必须 %1s 更新您的固定链接结构 %2s 为除“普通”以外的其他内容，以便系列目录 URL 正常工作。','Series Per Page:'=>'每页系列：','Series Table of Contents Title:'=>'系列目录标题：','Series Icons'=>'系列图标','Width for icon on series table of contents page (in pixels)'=>'系列目录页面上图标的宽度（以像素为单位）','Width for icon on a post page (in pixels).'=>'帖子页面上图标的宽度（以像素为单位）。','Width for icon if displayed via the latest series template (in pixels).'=>'如果通过最新系列模板显示，图标的宽度（以像素为单位）。','Latest Series'=>'最新系列','This display is used by the "Latest Series" widget.'=>'此显示由 "最新系列" widget 使用。','Latest Series (tags before):'=>'最新系列（之前的标签）：','Latest Series (inner tags):'=>'最新系列（内部标签）：','Latest Series (tags after):'=>'最新系列（标签在后）：','This display is used by the "Series Table of Contents" widget, shortcode, and URL.'=>'此显示由“系列目录”小部件、短代码和 URL 使用。','This display is used by the "Series Table of Contents". To find the URL for this display, go the "Display" tab and then "Series Table of Contents URL".'=>'此显示由“系列目录”使用。要找到此显示的 URL，请转到“显示”标签，然后选择“系列目录 URL”。','These settings allow you to customize the metabox on the post editing screen.'=>'这些设置允许您自定义帖子编辑屏幕上的元框。','Default Series Order'=>'默认系列顺序','Alphabetical A-Z'=>'字母顺序 A-Z','Alphabetical Z-A'=>'字母顺序 Z-A','Show "Add New"'=>'显示 "添加新项"','Show "Post title in widget"'=>'显示 "widget 中的帖子标题"','Metabox Series Order'=>'元框系列顺序','Post Details Settings'=>'帖子详情设置','Configure the Series Post Details display shown on posts in a series.'=>'配置在系列帖子中显示的系列帖子详情。','As in Template'=>'如模板中所示','Display Series Post Details?'=>'显示系列帖子详情？','Post Details Selection'=>'帖子详情选择','Edit this layout'=>'编辑此布局','Loading…'=>'加载中…','Post Details Position'=>'帖子详情位置','Series Meta Template'=>'系列元模板','Series Meta (with excerpts)'=>'系列元（带摘录）','Limit to single page only'=>'仅限单页','Whether to limit series meta display to single page only or include archive page.'=>'是否仅限于单页显示系列元数据，或包括归档页面。','Post List Box Settings'=>'帖子列表框设置','Configure the Post List Box that displays all posts in a series.'=>'配置显示系列中所有帖子的帖子列表框。','Display Post List Boxes?'=>'显示帖子列表框？','Post List Boxes Selection'=>'帖子列表框选择','Edit this box'=>'编辑此框','Post List Box Position'=>'帖子列表框位置','Series Post List Template'=>'系列帖子列表模板','Post Title (Linked Post)'=>'帖子标题（链接帖子）','Post Title (Current Post)'=>'帖子标题（当前帖子）','Navigation'=>'导航','Navigation Settings'=>'导航设置','Configure the Series Navigation display shown on posts in a series.'=>'配置在系列中显示的系列导航。','Display Series Navigation?'=>'显示系列导航？','Navigation Selection'=>'导航选择','Navigation Position'=>'导航位置','Navigation Template'=>'导航模板','Next Post Text'=>'下一篇帖子文本','Previous Post Text'=>'上一篇帖子文本','First Post Text'=>'第一篇文章文本','Post Types'=>'post type','Custom Post Type Support'=>'自定义文章类型支持','Enable PublishPress Series for custom post types.'=>'为自定义文章类型启用 PublishPress Series。','Pro Features'=>'专业功能','These settings allow you enable or disable features in PublishPress Series Pro.'=>'这些设置允许您启用或禁用 PublishPress Series Pro 中的功能。','Allow custom post types to be used with PublishPress Series.'=>'允许将自定义文章类型与 PublishPress Series 一起使用。','Shortcodes'=>'短代码','Provides shortcodes to display series information.'=>'提供短代码以显示系列信息。','Extra Tokens'=>'额外标记','Provides extra tokens to customize the output of series information.'=>'提供额外标记以自定义系列信息的输出。','Multiple Series'=>'多个系列','Allows authors to add posts to more than one series.'=>'允许作者将文章添加到多个系列中。','Series Category'=>'系列类别','Settings for Series Categories archive URL and display behavior.'=>'系列类别存档 URL 和显示行为的设置。','Series Categories URL Base:'=>'系列类别 URL 基础：','This text will be used in Series Categories archive URLs. If you change it, old URLs will be redirected to the new base.'=>'此文本将在系列分类归档 URL 中使用。如果您更改它，旧的 URL 将重定向到新的基础 URL。','Series Categories Archive Template:'=>'系列类别存档模板：','Use template from Theme'=>'使用主题中的模板','Use template from Plugin'=>'使用插件中的模板','Theme template uses your active theme template hierarchy. Plugin template uses PublishPress Series fallback design when your theme does not provide taxonomy-series_group.php.'=>'主题模板使用您当前激活的主题模板层次结构。当您的主题未提供 taxonomy-series_group.php 时，插件模板使用 PublishPress Series 回退设计。','Plugin Template Display Options:'=>'插件模板显示选项：','Show Series Icon'=>'显示系列图标','Show Series Description'=>'显示系列描述','Show Posts in each Series as list items'=>'以列表项的形式显示每个系列的帖子','This feature allows you to create a new taxonomy for this plugin to use if you don\'t want to use the default "Series" taxonomy.'=>'此功能允许您为此插件创建一个新的分类法，如果您不想使用默认的“系列”分类法。','Series Taxonomy Slug:'=>'系列分类法标识符：','This text will be part of the series base URL.'=>'此文本将成为系列基本 URL 的一部分。','Series Taxonomy:'=>'系列分类法：','To create a new taxonomy, enter the new name and click the "Update Options" button.'=>'要创建新的分类法，请输入新名称并单击“更新选项”按钮。','Migrate Terms'=>'迁移术语','Automatically migrate existing series terms to the new taxonomy'=>'自动将现有的系列术语迁移到新的分类法','If checked, all terms from the current taxonomy will be migrated to the new taxonomy when you change the taxonomy slug. If unchecked, only the taxonomy slug will be changed.'=>'如果选中，则在您更改分类法别名时，当前分类法中的所有术语将迁移到新的分类法。如果未选中，则仅更改分类法别名。','Sorry, no results found.'=>'抱歉，未找到结果。','You\'re using PublishPress Series Free. The Pro version has more features and support. %sUpgrade to Pro%s'=>'您正在使用 PublishPress Series 免费版。专业版具有更多功能和支持。%s升级到专业版%s','Upgrade to Pro'=>'升级到专业版','Need PublishPress Series Support?'=>'需要 PublishPress Series 支持吗？','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'如果您需要帮助或有新的功能请求，请告诉我们。','Request Support'=>'请求支持','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'详细文档也可在插件网站上获取。','View Knowledge Base'=>'查看知识库','An error occured'=>'发生错误','%1$s series migrated to new taxonomy'=>'%1$s 系列已迁移到新 taxonomy','If you like %s, please leave us a %s rating. Thank you!'=>'如果你喜欢 %s，请给我们留下一个 %s 评分。谢谢！','About PublishPress Series'=>'关于 PublishPress 系列','About'=>'关于','PublishPress Series Documentation'=>'PublishPress 系列文档','Documentation'=>'文档','Contact the PublishPress team'=>'联系 PublishPress 团队','Contact'=>'联系','Sorry but you don\'t have permission to add series'=>'抱歉，您没有权限添加系列','The name you picked isn\'t sanitizing correctly. Try something different.'=>'您选择的名称未正确清理。请尝试其他名称。','Hmm... it looks like there is already a series with that name. Try something else'=>'嗯……看起来已经有一个同名的系列。试试其他名称','Not part of a series'=>'不属于任何系列','Search series'=>'搜索系列','Series Part:'=>'系列部分：','Post title in widget:'=>'小部件中的帖子标题：','A short title of this post that will be used in the Series widget. Leave blank to use the full title.'=>'此帖的短标题将用于系列小部件。留空以使用完整标题。','<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a> (No part number)'=>'<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a>（无部分编号）','<a href="%3$s" title="%4$s">%5$s</a> (Part %1$s of %2$s)'=>'<a href="%3$s" title="%4$s">%5$s</a>（%2$s 的第 %1$s 部分）','<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a>  (No Part Number)'=>'<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a>  (无部件编号)','No Series'=>'无系列','View all series'=>'查看所有系列','Manage All Series'=>'管理所有系列','Term Order'=>'术语顺序','To reposition an item, drag and drop the row by "clicking and holding" it anywhere and moving it to its new position.'=>'要重新定位项目，请通过“单击并按住”该行的任何位置进行拖放，将其移动到新位置。','ID'=>'ID','Terms are usually ordered alphabetically, but you can choose your own order by entering a number (1 for first, etc.) in this field.'=>'条目通常按字母顺序排列，但您可以通过在此字段中输入一个数字（1为第一，等等）选择自己的顺序。','Current series icon:'=>'当前系列图标：','No icon currently'=>'当前没有图标','Delete image? (note: there will not be an image associated with this series if you select this)'=>'删除图片？（注意：如果选择此项，则该系列将不再关联任何图片）','Series Icon Upload:'=>'系列图标上传：','Upload an image for the series.'=>'上传一个系列的图像。','Invalid form data'=>'无效的表单数据','Invalid nonce, reload and try again'=>'无效的 nonce，重新加载并重试','Invalid taxonomy'=>'无效的 taxonomy','Not enough permission'=>'权限不足','Updated successfully'=>'已成功更新','Settings'=>'设置','PublishPress Series Options'=>'PublishPress 系列选项','Taxonomy'=>'分类法','Metabox'=>'Metabox','Advanced'=>'高级','Select "Not part of a series" to remove any series data from post'=>'选择“不是系列的一部分”以从帖子中删除任何系列数据','&larr; Go to Series'=>'&larr; 转到系列','View Series'=>'查看系列','Series List'=>'系列列表','Series Link'=>'系列链接','A link to a Series'=>'指向系列的链接','Series Navigation'=>'系列导航','Series: '=>'系列: ','Posts from the series: '=>'来自系列的帖子: ','Series:'=>'系列:','Part:'=>'部分:','All the Series I\'ve Written'=>'我写过的所有系列','<a href="%s" title="%s">Series</a>'=>'<a href="%s" title="%s">系列</a>','Auto/None'=>'自动/无','Use this to control the output of the latest series widget'=>'使用此选项控制最新系列小部件的输出','Most Recent Series'=>'最近系列','Title:'=>'标题:','The layout and content of this widget can be adjusted via the <a href="%s">Latest Series</a> area.'=>'此widget的布局和内容可以通过<a href="%s">最新系列</a>区域进行调整。','Hide series with no posts?'=>'隐藏没有帖子系列？','Order by:'=>'排序依据：','Number of posts in Series'=>'系列中的帖子数量','Name of Series'=>'系列名称','Series Slug'=>'系列别名','When Series was Created'=>'系列创建时间','Random'=>'随机','Number of series to display:'=>'要显示的系列数量：','Display Order: '=>'显示顺序： ','ASC: '=>'升序： ','DESC: '=>'降序： ','Use this to display the Series Table of contents'=>'使用此选项显示系列目录','Select Series'=>'选择系列','Other posts in series:'=>'系列中的其他帖子：','Show Series Table Of Content'=>'显示系列目录','Show Series Table Of Content as:'=>'将系列目录显示为：','Dropdown:'=>'下拉菜单：','List:'=>'列表：','Show post count:'=>'显示帖子数量：','Hide empty series:'=>'隐藏空系列：','name'=>'name','count'=>'count','slug'=>'slug','series id'=>'series id','Order:'=>'订单：','Exclude series:'=>'排除系列：','Include series:'=>'包含系列：','Number of Series:'=>'系列数量：','Offset:'=>'偏移量：','You can select the offset for the number of series (useful for paging).  No offset if left blank'=>'您可以选择系列数量的偏移量（对分页有用）。如果留空，则没有偏移量','Search:'=>'搜索：','You can return any series that match this search string (matched against series names)'=>'您可以返回与此搜索字符串匹配的任何系列（与系列名称匹配）','Show other posts in the current series:'=>'显示当前系列中的其他帖子：','Current series'=>'当前系列','Series widget title:'=>'系列小部件标题：','This text will display above other posts in this series.'=>'此文本将在此系列中的其他帖子上方显示。','<strong>This plugin can be deleted.</strong>'=>'<strong>此插件可以被删除。</strong>','The %1$s already has a parameter indexed with the name: %2$s.'=>'%1$s 已经有一个以名称 %2$s 索引的参数。','The %1$s method can only be used to register a child of %2$s.'=>'%1$s 方法只能用于注册 %2$s 的子类。','Unable to retrieve an instance of %1$s. Not found.'=>'无法检索到 %1$s 的实例。未找到。','%1$s is not a valid entity (expected: %2$s).'=>'%1$s 不是有效的实体（预期：%2$s）。','The "%1$s" file is either missing or could not be read due to permissions. Please ensure that the following path is correct and verify that the file permissions are correct:%2$s %3$s'=>'“%1$s”文件丢失或由于权限问题无法读取。请确保以下路径正确并验证文件权限是否正确：%2$s %3$s','%s does not exist or is not reachable.'=>'%s 不存在或无法访问。','Nonce fail.'=>'Nonce 失败。','The provided object fully qualified class name (%1$s) must implement the %2$s interface.'=>'提供的对象完全限定类名（%1$s）必须实现%2$s接口。','The given file path (%s) is not readable.'=>'给定的文件路径 (%s) 不能读取。','An error occurred, please try again.'=>'发生错误，请重试。','The incoming value for %1$s is expected to be a closure.  It was not.'=>'%1$s 的传入值预期为闭包，但不是。','Deactivate License'=>'停用许可证','Activate License'=>'激活许可证','License Key successfully activated.'=>'许可证密钥成功激活。','License Key successfully deactivated.'=>'许可证密钥成功停用。','The value for %1$s is already set and it is not an array. The %2$s method can only be used to push values to this data element when it is an array.'=>'%1$s的值已设置，并且不是数组。当它是数组时，%2$s方法只能用于将值推送到此数据元素。','The value for %1$s already exists in the %2$s property. Overrides are not allowed. Since the value of this data is an array, you may want to use the %3$s method to push your value to the array.'=>'%1$s的值已存在于%2$s属性中。禁止覆盖。由于此数据的值是数组，您可能想使用%3$s方法将您的值推送到数组中。','The value for %1$s already exists in the %2$s property. Overrides are not allowed.  Consider attaching your value to a different key'=>'%1$s的值已存在于%2$s属性中。禁止覆盖。考虑将您的值附加到不同的键','The namespace for this manifest file has already been registered, choose a namespace other than %s'=>'此清单文件的命名空间已注册，请选择其他命名空间而不是%s','The provided value for %1$s is not a valid url.  The url provided was: %2$s'=>'提供的 %1$s 值不是有效的 URL。提供的 URL 是：%2$s','License Key for %1$s'=>'%1$s 的许可证密钥','Enter your license key: '=>'输入您的许可证密钥：','taxonomy general nameSeries Categories'=>'系列类别','taxonomy general nameSeries'=>'系列','taxonomy singular nameSeries Category'=>'系列类别','taxonomy singular nameSeries'=>'系列','series grouping column headerSeries'=>'系列','Post List Box post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','singular post list box post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','custom layout post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s','series meta box titleSeries'=>'系列','posts list column headerSeries'=>'系列','dashboard count labelSeries'=>'系列','top-level admin menu labelSeries'=>'系列','taxonomy menu nameSeries'=>'系列','leave the %tokens% as is when translatingThis entry is part %series_part% of %total_posts_in_series% in the series '=>'此条目是系列中 %series_part% 的 %total_posts_in_series% 部分 ','series list titleSeries'=>'系列','widget title defaultSeries'=>'系列','widget section labelSeries'=>'系列']];